cached.description: If true will cache the readed file within the cache object.

fileName.description: A fileName used in different calls and configs like @FileConfig or @DirectoryConfig.

filePath.description: A filePath used in different calls and configs like @FileConfig or @DirectoryConfig.

rolePermissions.description: Lists for the different roles e.g. guest for write. Central point add permissions to a configuration. Dependent of the permission type of a call a certain list wll be selected. When ist write with role guest then no exception is thrown.

module.description: Defines a target module where generating occurs.

moduleScope.description: Defines scope of the configuration within module, eg 'test' or 'main' .

scope.description: A scope for the cache value.

creationDate.description: Used to define the creation of an item.

description.description: A description of the model used by every model extending BaseClassImpl.

id.description: The numeric id of an instance of a class.

sheetName.description: A name for the sheet selected.
